{"markdown":{"yaml":{"format":"html"},"containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"aws-page\">\n\n  <div class=\"wd-hero content-section\" style=\"padding-top: 4rem; padding-bottom: 2rem;\">\n\n    <div class=\"wd-hero-copy\">\n      \n      <div class=\"wd-hero-title\">\n        Master<br>\n        <span class=\"accent\">Amazon</span><br>\n        <span class=\"aws-text\">Web Services</span>\n      </div>\n      \n      <p class=\"wd-hero-subtitle\">\n        A structured, practitioner-built program covering cloud fundamentals,\n        core AWS services, Docker containerisation, and production deployment \n        — from absolute zero to job-ready.\n      </p>\n\n      <div class=\"hero-note\">\n        <span style=\"color: var(--color-orange); font-weight: bold;\">//</span> Starts with cloud basics. No prior experience required.\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"wd-hero-actions\">\n        <a href=\"/contact.qmd\" class=\"btn-primary-wd\">Start Learning</a>\n        <a href=\"#modules\" class=\"btn-ghost-wd\">View Curriculum ↓</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"wd-hero-visual\" style=\"position: relative;\">\n      <div class=\"aws-hero-services\">\n        <div class=\"aws-svc-pill\"><div class=\"svc-icon\">☁️</div><div><div class=\"svc-name\">EC2</div><div class=\"svc-cat\">Compute</div></div></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-svc-pill\"><div class=\"svc-icon\">🪣</div><div><div class=\"svc-name\">S3</div><div class=\"svc-cat\">Storage</div></div></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-svc-pill\"><div class=\"svc-icon docker\">🐳</div><div><div class=\"svc-name\">Docker</div><div class=\"svc-cat\">Containers</div></div></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-svc-pill\"><div class=\"svc-icon\">🔒</div><div><div class=\"svc-name\">IAM</div><div class=\"svc-cat\">Identity &amp; Access</div></div></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-svc-pill\"><div class=\"svc-icon\">🌐</div><div><div class=\"svc-name\">VPC</div><div class=\"svc-cat\">Networking</div></div></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-svc-pill\"><div class=\"svc-icon green\">λ</div><div><div class=\"svc-name\">Lambda</div><div class=\"svc-cat\">Serverless</div></div></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n  \n  <section class=\"tools-strip content-section\" style=\"margin-top: 1rem; padding-top: 2rem; padding-bottom: 4rem;\">\n    <div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n      <div class=\"tools-label\">Learning Phases</div>\n      <div class=\"tools-row\">\n        <span class=\"tool-box\"><span class=\"dot\"></span>Cloud Fundamentals</span>\n        <span class=\"tool-box\"><span class=\"dot\"></span>AWS Core Services</span>\n        <span class=\"tool-box\"><span class=\"dot\"></span>Docker &amp; Containers</span>\n        <span class=\"tool-box\"><span class=\"dot\"></span>Web Deployment</span>\n        <span class=\"tool-box\"><span class=\"dot\"></span>Serverless Architecture</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  \n  <section class=\"content-section\" style=\"padding-top: 0;\">\n    <div style=\"max-width: 100%; margin-bottom: 4rem;\">\n      <div class=\"section-label\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Learning Path</div>\n      <h2 class=\"section-title\">Your Road to AWS Mastery</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-body\">\n        Five progressive phases — engineered so each week builds directly on the last, from cloud theory to certified practitioner.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"aws-timeline\">\n      <div class=\"aws-step\">\n        <div class=\"aws-dot\"></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-content\">\n          <h4>Cloud Computing Fundamentals</h4>\n          <p>IaaS, PaaS, SaaS, cloud economics, and the why behind cloud migration.</p>\n          <span class=\"aws-duration\">⏱ Weeks 1–2</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"aws-step\">\n        <div class=\"aws-dot\"></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-content\">\n          <h4>AWS Core: Compute &amp; Networking</h4>\n          <p>EC2, S3, VPC, IAM — launching and securing real infrastructure.</p>\n          <span class=\"aws-duration\">⏱ Weeks 3–4</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"aws-step\">\n        <div class=\"aws-dot\"></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-content\">\n          <h4>Docker &amp; Containerisation</h4>\n          <p>Build images, compose multi-service apps, and push to ECR.</p>\n          <span class=\"aws-duration\">⏱ Weeks 5–6</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"aws-step\">\n        <div class=\"aws-dot\"></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-content\">\n          <h4>Web Deployment &amp; Serverless</h4>\n          <p>Nginx on EC2, SSL, Lambda, API Gateway, and event-driven patterns.</p>\n          <span class=\"aws-duration\">⏱ Weeks 7–9</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"aws-step\">\n        <div class=\"aws-dot\" style=\"background: #f59e0b; box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px var(--page-bg), 0 0 0 8px rgba(245,158,11,0.2);\"></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-content\">\n          <h4>Capstone + Certification Prep</h4>\n          <p>Deploy a full production app and prepare for SAA-C03.</p>\n          <span class=\"aws-duration\" style=\"color: #f59e0b; border-color: rgba(245,158,11,0.3);\">🏆 Week 10 — Cert Ready</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  \n  <section id=\"modules\" class=\"content-section\" style=\"padding-top: 2rem;\">\n    <div style=\"max-width: 100%; margin-bottom: 3rem;\">\n      <div class=\"section-label\">Curriculum</div>\n      <h2 class=\"section-title\">Five Core Modules</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-body\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">\n        Each module is a self-contained, hands-on unit with labs on real AWS infrastructure — not simulated environments.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"aws-modules-grid\">\n\n      <div class=\"aws-mod-card mod-1\" data-num=\"01\">\n        <div class=\"mod-header\">\n          <div class=\"mod-icon\">☁️</div>\n          <h3 class=\"mod-title\">Cloud Fundamentals</h3>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"mod-desc\">Build the mental model every cloud practitioner needs. Understand how cloud providers work, what you pay for, and why cloud has replaced on-premise infrastructure.</p>\n        <div class=\"mod-topics-expand\">\n          <div class=\"mod-topics-inner\">\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">IaaS, PaaS &amp; SaaS</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">Cloud economics</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">AWS global infrastructure</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">Shared Responsibility</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"aws-mod-card mod-2\" data-num=\"02\">\n        <div class=\"mod-header\">\n          <div class=\"mod-icon\">⚙️</div>\n          <h3 class=\"mod-title\">AWS Core Services</h3>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"mod-desc\">Get hands on with the services that power 70% of cloud workloads. Launch EC2 instances, configure secure networks, store objects in S3, and lock down IAM.</p>\n        <div class=\"mod-topics-expand\">\n          <div class=\"mod-topics-inner\">\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">EC2 &amp; AMIs</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">S3 policies</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">VPC &amp; subnets</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">IAM roles</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"aws-mod-card mod-3\" data-num=\"03\">\n        <div class=\"mod-header\">\n          <div class=\"mod-icon\">🐳</div>\n          <h3 class=\"mod-title\">Docker &amp; Containers</h3>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"mod-desc\">Package your applications once, run them anywhere. Master Docker from first principles and integrate containers natively into AWS using ECR and ECS.</p>\n        <div class=\"mod-topics-expand\">\n          <div class=\"mod-topics-inner\">\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">Docker architecture</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">Dockerfiles</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">Amazon ECR</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">ECS Fargate</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"aws-mod-card mod-4\" data-num=\"04\">\n        <div class=\"mod-header\">\n          <div class=\"mod-icon\">🌐</div>\n          <h3 class=\"mod-title\">Web &amp; Serverless</h3>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"mod-desc\">Take real applications live. Configure Nginx on EC2, automate SSL with Let's Encrypt, build APIs with Lambda, and connect services with event patterns.</p>\n        <div class=\"mod-topics-expand\">\n          <div class=\"mod-topics-inner\">\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">Nginx proxy</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">SSL / Let's Encrypt</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">Route 53 DNS</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">AWS Lambda</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"aws-mod-card mod-1 wide-card\" data-num=\"05\">\n        <div class=\"mod-header\">\n          <div class=\"mod-icon\">🏗️</div>\n          <h3 class=\"mod-title\">Architecture &amp; Cert Prep</h3>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"mod-desc\">Tie everything together. Design scalable architectures using AWS Well-Architected Framework pillars. Add managed databases, caching, and monitoring — then build a complete capstone project.</p>\n        <div class=\"mod-topics-expand\">\n          <div class=\"mod-topics-inner\">\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">RDS backups &amp; replicas</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">Load Balancers</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">Auto Scaling</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">CloudWatch</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">SAA-C03 mock tests</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n  </section>\n    \n    \n  \n  <section class=\"content-section\" style=\"padding-top: 4rem;\">\n    <div style=\"text-align: left; margin-bottom: 3rem;\">\n      <div class=\"section-label\" style=\"justify-content: left;\">Services</div>\n      <h2 class=\"section-title\">AWS Services You'll Learn</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-body\" style=\"margin: 0 auto;\">\n        Hands-on labs with the most in-demand AWS services — grouped by category so you understand how they interconnect.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"aws-svc-categories\">\n      <div class=\"aws-cat-card\">\n        <div class=\"aws-cat-header\"><div class=\"cat-icon\">⚡</div><h4>Compute</h4></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-svc-list\"><span class=\"tool-box\">EC2</span><span class=\"tool-box\">Lambda</span><span class=\"tool-box\">ECS Fargate</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"aws-cat-card\">\n        <div class=\"aws-cat-header\"><div class=\"cat-icon\">🗃️</div><h4>Storage &amp; DBs</h4></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-svc-list\"><span class=\"tool-box\">S3</span><span class=\"tool-box\">EBS</span><span class=\"tool-box\">RDS</span><span class=\"tool-box\">DynamoDB</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"aws-cat-card\">\n        <div class=\"aws-cat-header\"><div class=\"cat-icon\">🌐</div><h4>Networking</h4></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-svc-list\"><span class=\"tool-box\">VPC</span><span class=\"tool-box\">Route 53</span><span class=\"tool-box\">ALB / NLB</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"aws-cat-card\">\n        <div class=\"aws-cat-header\"><div class=\"cat-icon\">🔒</div><h4>Security</h4></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-svc-list\"><span class=\"tool-box\">IAM</span><span class=\"tool-box\">Security Groups</span><span class=\"tool-box\">KMS</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"aws-cat-card\">\n        <div class=\"aws-cat-header\"><div class=\"cat-icon\">📊</div><h4>Monitoring</h4></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-svc-list\"><span class=\"tool-box\">CloudWatch</span><span class=\"tool-box\">CloudTrail</span><span class=\"tool-box\">SNS</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"aws-cat-card\">\n        <div class=\"aws-cat-header\"><div class=\"cat-icon\">🐳</div><h4>Containers</h4></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-svc-list\"><span class=\"tool-box\">Docker</span><span class=\"tool-box\">ECR</span><span class=\"tool-box\">ECS</span></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  \n  <section class=\"content-section\" style=\"padding-top: 4rem;\">\n    <div style=\"max-width: 100%; margin-bottom: 3rem;\">\n      <div class=\"section-label\">Hands-On Projects</div>\n      <h2 class=\"section-title\">Build Real Things</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-body\">\n        Every module culminates in a project deployed to live AWS infrastructure — not sandboxed demos.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"aws-projects-grid\">\n      <div class=\"proj-card shape-1\">\n        <span class=\"proj-num\">Project 01</span>\n        <h4 class=\"proj-name\">Secure Multi-Tier VPC</h4>\n        <p class=\"proj-desc\">Design and deploy a VPC with public/private subnets, NAT gateways, bastion host, and security group rules.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"proj-card shape-2\">\n        <span class=\"proj-num\">Project 02</span>\n        <h4 class=\"proj-name\">App on ECS Fargate</h4>\n        <p class=\"proj-desc\">Dockerise a web application, push to ECR, and deploy as a managed ECS Fargate service behind an ALB.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"proj-card shape-2\">\n        <span class=\"proj-num\">Project 03</span>\n        <h4 class=\"proj-name\">Serverless REST API</h4>\n        <p class=\"proj-desc\">Build an API using Lambda + API Gateway backed by DynamoDB, with IAM-secured endpoints.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"proj-card shape-1\">\n        <span class=\"proj-num\">Project 04</span>\n        <h4 class=\"proj-name\">Global Static Website</h4>\n        <p class=\"proj-desc\">Host a site on S3, front it with CloudFront CDN, attach an ACM SSL certificate, and configure Route 53.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"proj-card shape-1\">\n        <span class=\"proj-num\">Project 05</span>\n        <h4 class=\"proj-name\">Auto-Scaling Web App</h4>\n        <p class=\"proj-desc\">Deploy an app across multiple AZs with an ALB, Auto Scaling Group, RDS Multi-AZ, and CloudWatch alarms.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"proj-card shape-2\">\n        <span class=\"proj-num\">Capstone</span>\n        <h4 class=\"proj-name\">Production Platform</h4>\n        <p class=\"proj-desc\">Synthesise all modules into a single full-stack platform: containers, databases, monitoring, and CI/CD.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  \n  <section class=\"content-section\" style=\"padding-top: 4rem;\">\n    <div style=\"max-width: 100%; margin-bottom: 3rem;\">\n      <div class=\"section-label\">Coming Soon</div>\n      <h2 class=\"section-title\">More Cloud Providers on the Way</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-body\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">\n        AWS is just the beginning. Dedicated tracks for Google Cloud and Azure are currently being developed — with the same hands-on, practitioner-first approach.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"aws-teaser-row\">\n      <div class=\"teaser-card active\">\n        <div class=\"t-logo\">Amazon Web Services</div>\n        <div class=\"t-status\">● Now Enrolling</div>\n        <div class=\"t-info\">Full curriculum live. Certification aligned to SAA-C03.</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"teaser-card\">\n        <div class=\"t-logo\">Google Cloud Platform</div>\n        <div class=\"t-status\" style=\"color: var(--text-dim);\">◌ In Development</div>\n        <div class=\"t-info\">GCP Associate Cloud Engineer track — launching soon.</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"teaser-card\">\n        <div class=\"t-logo\">Microsoft Azure</div>\n        <div class=\"t-status\" style=\"color: var(--text-dim);\">◌ Planned</div>\n        <div class=\"t-info\">AZ-900 &amp; AZ-104 aligned track coming later this year.</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"teaser-card\">\n        <div class=\"t-logo\">Multi-Cloud Architecture</div>\n        <div class=\"t-status\" style=\"color: var(--text-dim);\">◌ Advanced Track</div>\n        <div class=\"t-info\">Advanced course on designing for multiple CSPs simultaneously.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  \n  <div class=\"enrollment-badge\">\n    <span class=\"blink-dot\"></span> Limited Seats Per Cohort\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"wd-cta content-section\" style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 5rem;\">\n    <h2>Your first AWS project goes live <em>this month.</em></h2>\n    <p>\n      Structured training, real infrastructure, live projects you can put in a portfolio — and a clear path to your first AWS certification.\n    </p>\n    <div class=\"wd-cta-actions\">\n      <a href=\"/contact.qmd\" class=\"btn-primary-wd\">Enroll in AWS Track →</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n```\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"aws-page\">\n\n  <div class=\"wd-hero content-section\" style=\"padding-top: 4rem; padding-bottom: 2rem;\">\n\n    <div class=\"wd-hero-copy\">\n      \n      <div class=\"wd-hero-title\">\n        Master<br>\n        <span class=\"accent\">Amazon</span><br>\n        <span class=\"aws-text\">Web Services</span>\n      </div>\n      \n      <p class=\"wd-hero-subtitle\">\n        A structured, practitioner-built program covering cloud fundamentals,\n        core AWS services, Docker containerisation, and production deployment \n        — from absolute zero to job-ready.\n      </p>\n\n      <div class=\"hero-note\">\n        <span style=\"color: var(--color-orange); font-weight: bold;\">//</span> Starts with cloud basics. No prior experience required.\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"wd-hero-actions\">\n        <a href=\"/contact.qmd\" class=\"btn-primary-wd\">Start Learning</a>\n        <a href=\"#modules\" class=\"btn-ghost-wd\">View Curriculum ↓</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"wd-hero-visual\" style=\"position: relative;\">\n      <div class=\"aws-hero-services\">\n        <div class=\"aws-svc-pill\"><div class=\"svc-icon\">☁️</div><div><div class=\"svc-name\">EC2</div><div class=\"svc-cat\">Compute</div></div></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-svc-pill\"><div class=\"svc-icon\">🪣</div><div><div class=\"svc-name\">S3</div><div class=\"svc-cat\">Storage</div></div></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-svc-pill\"><div class=\"svc-icon docker\">🐳</div><div><div class=\"svc-name\">Docker</div><div class=\"svc-cat\">Containers</div></div></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-svc-pill\"><div class=\"svc-icon\">🔒</div><div><div class=\"svc-name\">IAM</div><div class=\"svc-cat\">Identity &amp; Access</div></div></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-svc-pill\"><div class=\"svc-icon\">🌐</div><div><div class=\"svc-name\">VPC</div><div class=\"svc-cat\">Networking</div></div></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-svc-pill\"><div class=\"svc-icon green\">λ</div><div><div class=\"svc-name\">Lambda</div><div class=\"svc-cat\">Serverless</div></div></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n  \n  <section class=\"tools-strip content-section\" style=\"margin-top: 1rem; padding-top: 2rem; padding-bottom: 4rem;\">\n    <div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n      <div class=\"tools-label\">Learning Phases</div>\n      <div class=\"tools-row\">\n        <span class=\"tool-box\"><span class=\"dot\"></span>Cloud Fundamentals</span>\n        <span class=\"tool-box\"><span class=\"dot\"></span>AWS Core Services</span>\n        <span class=\"tool-box\"><span class=\"dot\"></span>Docker &amp; Containers</span>\n        <span class=\"tool-box\"><span class=\"dot\"></span>Web Deployment</span>\n        <span class=\"tool-box\"><span class=\"dot\"></span>Serverless Architecture</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  \n  <section class=\"content-section\" style=\"padding-top: 0;\">\n    <div style=\"max-width: 100%; margin-bottom: 4rem;\">\n      <div class=\"section-label\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Learning Path</div>\n      <h2 class=\"section-title\">Your Road to AWS Mastery</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-body\">\n        Five progressive phases — engineered so each week builds directly on the last, from cloud theory to certified practitioner.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"aws-timeline\">\n      <div class=\"aws-step\">\n        <div class=\"aws-dot\"></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-content\">\n          <h4>Cloud Computing Fundamentals</h4>\n          <p>IaaS, PaaS, SaaS, cloud economics, and the why behind cloud migration.</p>\n          <span class=\"aws-duration\">⏱ Weeks 1–2</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"aws-step\">\n        <div class=\"aws-dot\"></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-content\">\n          <h4>AWS Core: Compute &amp; Networking</h4>\n          <p>EC2, S3, VPC, IAM — launching and securing real infrastructure.</p>\n          <span class=\"aws-duration\">⏱ Weeks 3–4</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"aws-step\">\n        <div class=\"aws-dot\"></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-content\">\n          <h4>Docker &amp; Containerisation</h4>\n          <p>Build images, compose multi-service apps, and push to ECR.</p>\n          <span class=\"aws-duration\">⏱ Weeks 5–6</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"aws-step\">\n        <div class=\"aws-dot\"></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-content\">\n          <h4>Web Deployment &amp; Serverless</h4>\n          <p>Nginx on EC2, SSL, Lambda, API Gateway, and event-driven patterns.</p>\n          <span class=\"aws-duration\">⏱ Weeks 7–9</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"aws-step\">\n        <div class=\"aws-dot\" style=\"background: #f59e0b; box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px var(--page-bg), 0 0 0 8px rgba(245,158,11,0.2);\"></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-content\">\n          <h4>Capstone + Certification Prep</h4>\n          <p>Deploy a full production app and prepare for SAA-C03.</p>\n          <span class=\"aws-duration\" style=\"color: #f59e0b; border-color: rgba(245,158,11,0.3);\">🏆 Week 10 — Cert Ready</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  \n  <section id=\"modules\" class=\"content-section\" style=\"padding-top: 2rem;\">\n    <div style=\"max-width: 100%; margin-bottom: 3rem;\">\n      <div class=\"section-label\">Curriculum</div>\n      <h2 class=\"section-title\">Five Core Modules</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-body\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">\n        Each module is a self-contained, hands-on unit with labs on real AWS infrastructure — not simulated environments.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"aws-modules-grid\">\n\n      <div class=\"aws-mod-card mod-1\" data-num=\"01\">\n        <div class=\"mod-header\">\n          <div class=\"mod-icon\">☁️</div>\n          <h3 class=\"mod-title\">Cloud Fundamentals</h3>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"mod-desc\">Build the mental model every cloud practitioner needs. Understand how cloud providers work, what you pay for, and why cloud has replaced on-premise infrastructure.</p>\n        <div class=\"mod-topics-expand\">\n          <div class=\"mod-topics-inner\">\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">IaaS, PaaS &amp; SaaS</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">Cloud economics</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">AWS global infrastructure</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">Shared Responsibility</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"aws-mod-card mod-2\" data-num=\"02\">\n        <div class=\"mod-header\">\n          <div class=\"mod-icon\">⚙️</div>\n          <h3 class=\"mod-title\">AWS Core Services</h3>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"mod-desc\">Get hands on with the services that power 70% of cloud workloads. Launch EC2 instances, configure secure networks, store objects in S3, and lock down IAM.</p>\n        <div class=\"mod-topics-expand\">\n          <div class=\"mod-topics-inner\">\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">EC2 &amp; AMIs</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">S3 policies</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">VPC &amp; subnets</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">IAM roles</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"aws-mod-card mod-3\" data-num=\"03\">\n        <div class=\"mod-header\">\n          <div class=\"mod-icon\">🐳</div>\n          <h3 class=\"mod-title\">Docker &amp; Containers</h3>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"mod-desc\">Package your applications once, run them anywhere. Master Docker from first principles and integrate containers natively into AWS using ECR and ECS.</p>\n        <div class=\"mod-topics-expand\">\n          <div class=\"mod-topics-inner\">\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">Docker architecture</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">Dockerfiles</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">Amazon ECR</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">ECS Fargate</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"aws-mod-card mod-4\" data-num=\"04\">\n        <div class=\"mod-header\">\n          <div class=\"mod-icon\">🌐</div>\n          <h3 class=\"mod-title\">Web &amp; Serverless</h3>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"mod-desc\">Take real applications live. Configure Nginx on EC2, automate SSL with Let's Encrypt, build APIs with Lambda, and connect services with event patterns.</p>\n        <div class=\"mod-topics-expand\">\n          <div class=\"mod-topics-inner\">\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">Nginx proxy</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">SSL / Let's Encrypt</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">Route 53 DNS</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">AWS Lambda</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"aws-mod-card mod-1 wide-card\" data-num=\"05\">\n        <div class=\"mod-header\">\n          <div class=\"mod-icon\">🏗️</div>\n          <h3 class=\"mod-title\">Architecture &amp; Cert Prep</h3>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"mod-desc\">Tie everything together. Design scalable architectures using AWS Well-Architected Framework pillars. Add managed databases, caching, and monitoring — then build a complete capstone project.</p>\n        <div class=\"mod-topics-expand\">\n          <div class=\"mod-topics-inner\">\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">RDS backups &amp; replicas</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">Load Balancers</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">Auto Scaling</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">CloudWatch</span>\n            <span class=\"mod-topic\">SAA-C03 mock tests</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n  </section>\n    \n    \n  \n  <section class=\"content-section\" style=\"padding-top: 4rem;\">\n    <div style=\"text-align: left; margin-bottom: 3rem;\">\n      <div class=\"section-label\" style=\"justify-content: left;\">Services</div>\n      <h2 class=\"section-title\">AWS Services You'll Learn</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-body\" style=\"margin: 0 auto;\">\n        Hands-on labs with the most in-demand AWS services — grouped by category so you understand how they interconnect.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"aws-svc-categories\">\n      <div class=\"aws-cat-card\">\n        <div class=\"aws-cat-header\"><div class=\"cat-icon\">⚡</div><h4>Compute</h4></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-svc-list\"><span class=\"tool-box\">EC2</span><span class=\"tool-box\">Lambda</span><span class=\"tool-box\">ECS Fargate</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"aws-cat-card\">\n        <div class=\"aws-cat-header\"><div class=\"cat-icon\">🗃️</div><h4>Storage &amp; DBs</h4></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-svc-list\"><span class=\"tool-box\">S3</span><span class=\"tool-box\">EBS</span><span class=\"tool-box\">RDS</span><span class=\"tool-box\">DynamoDB</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"aws-cat-card\">\n        <div class=\"aws-cat-header\"><div class=\"cat-icon\">🌐</div><h4>Networking</h4></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-svc-list\"><span class=\"tool-box\">VPC</span><span class=\"tool-box\">Route 53</span><span class=\"tool-box\">ALB / NLB</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"aws-cat-card\">\n        <div class=\"aws-cat-header\"><div class=\"cat-icon\">🔒</div><h4>Security</h4></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-svc-list\"><span class=\"tool-box\">IAM</span><span class=\"tool-box\">Security Groups</span><span class=\"tool-box\">KMS</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"aws-cat-card\">\n        <div class=\"aws-cat-header\"><div class=\"cat-icon\">📊</div><h4>Monitoring</h4></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-svc-list\"><span class=\"tool-box\">CloudWatch</span><span class=\"tool-box\">CloudTrail</span><span class=\"tool-box\">SNS</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"aws-cat-card\">\n        <div class=\"aws-cat-header\"><div class=\"cat-icon\">🐳</div><h4>Containers</h4></div>\n        <div class=\"aws-svc-list\"><span class=\"tool-box\">Docker</span><span class=\"tool-box\">ECR</span><span class=\"tool-box\">ECS</span></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  \n  <section class=\"content-section\" style=\"padding-top: 4rem;\">\n    <div style=\"max-width: 100%; margin-bottom: 3rem;\">\n      <div class=\"section-label\">Hands-On Projects</div>\n      <h2 class=\"section-title\">Build Real Things</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-body\">\n        Every module culminates in a project deployed to live AWS infrastructure — not sandboxed demos.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"aws-projects-grid\">\n      <div class=\"proj-card shape-1\">\n        <span class=\"proj-num\">Project 01</span>\n        <h4 class=\"proj-name\">Secure Multi-Tier VPC</h4>\n        <p class=\"proj-desc\">Design and deploy a VPC with public/private subnets, NAT gateways, bastion host, and security group rules.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"proj-card shape-2\">\n        <span class=\"proj-num\">Project 02</span>\n        <h4 class=\"proj-name\">App on ECS Fargate</h4>\n        <p class=\"proj-desc\">Dockerise a web application, push to ECR, and deploy as a managed ECS Fargate service behind an ALB.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"proj-card shape-2\">\n        <span class=\"proj-num\">Project 03</span>\n        <h4 class=\"proj-name\">Serverless REST API</h4>\n        <p class=\"proj-desc\">Build an API using Lambda + API Gateway backed by DynamoDB, with IAM-secured endpoints.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"proj-card shape-1\">\n        <span class=\"proj-num\">Project 04</span>\n        <h4 class=\"proj-name\">Global Static Website</h4>\n        <p class=\"proj-desc\">Host a site on S3, front it with CloudFront CDN, attach an ACM SSL certificate, and configure Route 53.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"proj-card shape-1\">\n        <span class=\"proj-num\">Project 05</span>\n        <h4 class=\"proj-name\">Auto-Scaling Web App</h4>\n        <p class=\"proj-desc\">Deploy an app across multiple AZs with an ALB, Auto Scaling Group, RDS Multi-AZ, and CloudWatch alarms.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"proj-card shape-2\">\n        <span class=\"proj-num\">Capstone</span>\n        <h4 class=\"proj-name\">Production Platform</h4>\n        <p class=\"proj-desc\">Synthesise all modules into a single full-stack platform: containers, databases, monitoring, and CI/CD.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  \n  <section class=\"content-section\" style=\"padding-top: 4rem;\">\n    <div style=\"max-width: 100%; margin-bottom: 3rem;\">\n      <div class=\"section-label\">Coming Soon</div>\n      <h2 class=\"section-title\">More Cloud Providers on the Way</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-body\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">\n        AWS is just the beginning. Dedicated tracks for Google Cloud and Azure are currently being developed — with the same hands-on, practitioner-first approach.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"aws-teaser-row\">\n      <div class=\"teaser-card active\">\n        <div class=\"t-logo\">Amazon Web Services</div>\n        <div class=\"t-status\">● Now Enrolling</div>\n        <div class=\"t-info\">Full curriculum live. Certification aligned to SAA-C03.</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"teaser-card\">\n        <div class=\"t-logo\">Google Cloud Platform</div>\n        <div class=\"t-status\" style=\"color: var(--text-dim);\">◌ In Development</div>\n        <div class=\"t-info\">GCP Associate Cloud Engineer track — launching soon.</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"teaser-card\">\n        <div class=\"t-logo\">Microsoft Azure</div>\n        <div class=\"t-status\" style=\"color: var(--text-dim);\">◌ Planned</div>\n        <div class=\"t-info\">AZ-900 &amp; AZ-104 aligned track coming later this year.</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"teaser-card\">\n        <div class=\"t-logo\">Multi-Cloud Architecture</div>\n        <div class=\"t-status\" style=\"color: var(--text-dim);\">◌ Advanced Track</div>\n        <div class=\"t-info\">Advanced course on designing for multiple CSPs simultaneously.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  \n  <div class=\"enrollment-badge\">\n    <span class=\"blink-dot\"></span> Limited Seats Per Cohort\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"wd-cta content-section\" style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 5rem;\">\n    <h2>Your first AWS project goes live <em>this month.</em></h2>\n    <p>\n      Structured training, real infrastructure, live projects you can put in a portfolio — and a clear path to your first AWS certification.\n    </p>\n    <div class=\"wd-cta-actions\">\n      <a href=\"/contact.qmd\" class=\"btn-primary-wd\">Enroll in AWS Track →</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n```\n"},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true